    Summary: &quot;The life of Candy, a little orphan girl, and her friends.&quot;<br />
Run time: 1976-1979<br />
Genre‎: ‎Romance‎, historical drama<br />
<br />
What more is there to say about Candy Candy that hasn&#039;t been said already? Throughout the course of this series, you watch as characters grow, relationships blossom, adolescents coming of age and more. It will leave a long-lasting impression on you and a real impact for many reasons. It is instantly rewatchable.<br />
<br />
There&#039;s a lot of differences between the anime and the manga, of course, but relatively the original intent is kept within and shines through this one oh so well. Everything is done perfectly. <br />
<br />
It&#039;s an amazing delight. Please,

          <span style="display: none;" id="review341143">
        go watch it.
        
